          "extensions": [],
          "experiment_extension_reason": "PEPC is being introduced on Android as well in M134 and we wish to allow developers time to experiment with the feature on a mobile platform where the overall UX can be quite different and users interact with certain permissions differently.\n\nAdditionally there are still open questions around the markup of the element and whether it should be a void element vs allowing contents, and we would like to further explore options in this space before committing to one particular solution.",
